PrecisOrder (a) approving the transfer by the COMMISSIONER OF THE YUKON TERRITORY to the Solicitor General of Canada of the entire interest of the Crown in Lots 23 and 24 of Block 36, situate in the Town of WATSON LAKE, Yukon, in order to facilitate the operations of the ROYAL CANADIAN MOUNTED POLICE, and (b) IN EXCHANGE, to accept the transfer of the entire interest of the Crown in two other lots also situated in the Town of Watson Lake.
